{"tid":2118591,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"凱景名宿陳沛然報名立法會醫學界爭取連任","createTime":"2020-07-21T14:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T02:14:44.000Z","uid":7439,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3e788b03a4f90ec85e6ae27d7f5491bbbd8f60","tid":2118591,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2020/pdf/FC_ALLO_c.pdf?time=0.0566220546152969.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Flegco2020%2Fpdf%2FFC_ALLO_c.pdf%3Ftime%3D0.0566220546152969.pdf&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=66e9505e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2020/pdf/FC_ALLO_c.pdf?time=0.0566220546152969.pdf</a><br />\n醫學界 陳沛然 男 醫生 2020年7月21日 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1764/42831654201_7a50f67ee4_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1764%2F42831654201_7a50f67ee4_z.jpg&h=6f2a6e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/--cF9VLoqmJQ/XNwWBKXnnsI/AAAAAAAAdEw/Exv577PnvEUiVrSM4ywZEe6-WSz-ktxFwCLcBGAs/w1200-h630-p-k-no-nu/pierresoccer2019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F--cF9VLoqmJQ%2FXNwWBKXnnsI%2FAAAAAAAAdEw%2FExv577PnvEUiVrSM4ywZEe6-WSz-ktxFwCLcBGAs%2Fw1200-h630-p-k-no-nu%2Fpierresoccer2019.jpg&h=8de8f236&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a1391627db2643b6bc0b17dc9eeb43e0f17adcf","tid":2118591,"uid":7439,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7916/40125217393_5420e790f8_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7916%2F40125217393_5420e790f8_z.jpg&h=451ca7c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳沛然議員成功取得中國肺炎檢疫令數字：中台澳103543、外國69685(截至五月四日)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fswfGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fswfGS</a>"},{"pid":"4eb4a71cc94cedf738871145c182cda46eca484d","tid":2118591,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:20:32.000Z","msg":"2019-02-20<br />\n陳沛然：人口政策如何影響公共醫療？<br />\n<a href=\"https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/02/policy-affecting-public-medical-service.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F02%2Fpolicy-affecting-public-medical-service.html&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=e686e9d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/02/policy-affecting-public-medical-service.html</a>"},{"pid":"680fa7fff0b6b682f3d3f4957206927b2facebc1","tid":2118591,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"如果佢+其他34個泛民，算唔算成功左35+?"},{"pid":"e8a383373269b6d4fef9d8752a1d5bdd53830b09","tid":2118591,"uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"陳沛然醫生議員<br />\n1 天 &middot; <br />\n下午，去明報做Facebook live；<br />\n晚上，在Viu TV 做live show，19:30-19:40。<br />\n其實，我想去踢波，不過無得踢。<br />\n<br />\n陳沛然醫生議員在 Ruttonjee Hospital 。<br />\n11小時 &middot; Hong Kong &middot; <br />\n雖然今天放假，但是某些原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要回醫院做了一點工作。<br />\nWe stay at work for you. You stay at home for us and for HK."},{"pid":"9c4aeee038cd8b5959569175001ee1e29e44377e","tid":2118591,"uid":7439,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:22:32.000Z","msg":"直形容自己是中間派的現任醫學界立法會議員陳沛然表示，正積極考慮競選連任；對於部份民主派參與初選者簽署共同綱領，以否決財政預算案逼使特首回應五大訴求等，陳沛然指自己也認同這個方向：「一年前嘅6.12如果（政府）肯撤回（逃犯條例修訂），就唔需要討論到咁遠，令到個雪球越滾越大。」<br />\n<br />\n陳沛然表示，正積極考慮競逐連任醫學界立法會議員；<span class=\"red\">他直言由2016年開始參選第一日，已經公佈自己是中間偏黄</span>，於特首施政報告致謝動議案，2017年投了贊成票，2018年投下反對票；去年6.12前，已表明會於逃犯條例修訂案中投反對票。<br />\n<br />\n對於部份民主派參與初選者，簽署「當選後會否決財政預算案，逼使特首回應五大訴求」的共同綱領，<span class=\"red\">陳沛然表示，既然和平遊行等方法不獲政府理會，始終需要談判籌碼。他認同以否決財政預算案逼使政府談判的方向</span>：「中美貿易戰、制裁、都唔係香港可以處理到；對於立法會內部處理到嘅事情，<span class=\"red\">我同意用某啲方法去處理，否決財政預算案係其中一個埋枱傾嘅方法。</span>」"},{"pid":"c4540a49c0a20fb9c8af77d0bc49353f8c92f773","tid":2118591,"uid":34869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"我信陳醫生"},{"pid":"49146c1cb045bd2c79fa658efc15607b8c6649c4","tid":2118591,"uid":236414,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"874d8623be822115e4183e25e336f3dc5ce33fb5","tid":2118591,"uid":325346,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"而家個社會唔容納綠絲<br />\n個業界要你咩顏色就係咩顏色"},{"pid":"8eeb89fcdab2a5d8d2bf5d455c7568172bb86d5c","tid":2118591,"uid":70147,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"680fa7fff0b6b682f3d3f4957206927b2facebc1","tid":2118591,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"如果佢+其他34個泛民，算唔算成功左35+?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"佢中間派黎 唔係泛民"},{"pid":"90d19dfbc1ee8effeabe6ed6f8068aff5862d8a5","tid":2118591,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"我是一名足球員"},{"pid":"abba72c65b11d0e5b55255f6c114a49098d88b8f","tid":2118591,"uid":236414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:27:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"114a8dbb600636199d83070f91ce77e83a4d918a","tid":2118591,"uid":192409,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"8eeb89fcdab2a5d8d2bf5d455c7568172bb86d5c","tid":2118591,"uid":70147,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"680fa7fff0b6b682f3d3f4957206927b2facebc1","tid":2118591,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"如果佢+其他34個泛民，算唔算成功左35+?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"佢中間派黎 唔係泛民"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"但睇返上面佢段訪問 都幾黃下喎 話認同泛民提出否決財預算案"},{"pid":"9743bb955ea05